Package: marketdynamics
Title: Energy and Treasury Market Dynamics Dashboard
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R:
    person("Duncan", "McNabb", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "duncanmcnabb@ualberta.ca")
Description: A production-grade Shiny application built as a golem package
    for analyzing financial market dynamics across energy futures and US
    Treasury markets. Covers forward curve behavior, volatility surface,
    co-dynamics, seasonality, and hedge ratio dynamics.
